## ✅ Conclusion

The Credit Card Approval Prediction System demonstrates how machine learning can simplify and automate the credit card approval process. By analyzing applicant information and providing instant predictions through a Flask-based web application, the system reduces manual effort and supports faster decision-making. The project successfully combines data preprocessing, machine learning, and web development to create a practical and scalable solution. It also provides a strong foundation for future improvements such as cloud deployment, enhanced prediction accuracy, and additional financial analysis features.

